@startuml
left to right direction
actor "用户" as User
actor "平台管理员" as Admin

rectangle "系统" {
    usecase "意见反馈提交" as FeedbackSubmit
    usecase "反馈信息处理" as FeedbackProcess
    usecase "查看反馈记录及结果" as ViewFeedbackInfo
}

User --> FeedbackSubmit : 描述问题/建议并提交
FeedbackSubmit --> System : 传递反馈信息给管理员
Admin --> FeedbackProcess : 接收、整理反馈信息，优化改进平台
FeedbackProcess --> System : 记录处理情况

User --> ViewFeedbackInfo : 查看提交的反馈记录和处理结果
ViewFeedbackInfo --> System : 获取并展示相应信息
@enduml